    "causal_summary": "The 45-tile GLM-5.2 run (`../../004-bento-visuals`) sends every tile down a single generation path, but the score data shows two distinct layout primitives with a ~41-point gap: linear-flow tiles (table/timeline/list/donut/hero) score 86-94, while 2D-positioned tiles (matrix/node/routing/funnel/popover/connector-map/dense-chart) collapse to 35-58",
